1-FizzBuzz problem: For numbers 1 to 100, print "Fizz" for multiples of 3, "Buzz" for multiples of 5, and "FizzBuzz" for multiples of both.

iterate from 1-100

if(num%3==0 && num %5 ==0)
print "FrizzBuzz"

elseif(num%3 == 0)
print"Fizz"

elseif(num%5 == 0)
print"buzz"

else
print("Not divisible by 3 and 5)

